---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import HeroSection from '../components/HeroSection.astro';
import CTA from '../components/CTA.jsx';
---

<Layout
  title="Why Green Orbit Digital | Sustainable Space Marketing"
  description="Discover why forward-thinking space organisations choose Green Orbit Digital for sustainable, results-driven marketing, expertise, and innovative strategies."
>
  <Header />

  <main class="py-8">
    <HeroSection
      title="Why Choose Green Orbit Digital"
      description="We help space organisations grow sustainably. Here’s why our clients trust us to deliver measurable impact, innovation, and long-term success."
    />

    <section class="py-16 bg-secondary-500">
      <div class="container-custom space-y-24 text-white">

        <!-- Personalised Approach -->
        <div class="space-y-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center">Our Personalised Approach to Sustainable Marketing</h2>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl text-accent-500 font-semibold mb-2">Results-Driven, with Sustainability at Our Core</h3>
              <p class="mb-4">
                We focus on measurable results while prioritising sustainability. Every strategy we craft delivers growth that aligns with your environmental and business goals.
              </p>

              <h3 class="text-xl text-accent-500 font-semibold mb-2">Agency by Name, Partners by Nature</h3>
              <p class="mb-4">
                Acting as an extension of your team, we navigate your internal processes and deliver value at every stage, helping you succeed in complex space industry projects.
              </p>

              <h3 class="text-xl text-accent-500 font-semibold mb-2">Transparent and Open Communication</h3>
              <p class="mb-4">
                Honest conversations and rapid iteration are central to our approach. You’ll always know where we stand, and we’ll always act in your best interest.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-xl">
              <img src="/images/community.png" alt="Personalised approach illustration" class="w-full h-auto" />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Space Industry Expertise -->
        <div class="space-y-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center">Our Experience and Expertise in the Space Industry</h2>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
            <div class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-xl">
              <img src="/images/earth-observation.png" alt="Space industry expertise" class="w-full h-auto" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl text-accent-500 font-semibold mb-2">Real-World Space Industry Experience</h3>
              <p class="mb-4">
                We’ve worked across Earth observation, satellite technology, and beyond. We understand the challenges and nuances of your sector without needing extensive onboarding.
              </p>

              <h3 class="text-xl text-accent-500 font-semibold mb-2">Marketing Experts Who Understand the Sales Process</h3>
              <p class="mb-4">
                Our strategies are aligned with sales goals, ensuring marketing efforts directly contribute to revenue and measurable growth.
              </p>

              <h3 class="text-xl text-accent-500 font-semibold mb-2">We Speak Your Language</h3>
              <p class="mb-4">
                Combining space sector knowledge with marketing and sales expertise, we integrate these elements into strategies that fuel growth while keeping sustainability at the forefront.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Digital & Sustainable Expertise -->
        <div class="space-y-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center">Our Sustainable and Digital Expertise</h2>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl text-accent-500 font-semibold mb-2">Digital-First and Future-Ready</h3>
              <p class="mb-4">
                We embrace a digital-first philosophy using the latest tools and data insights to reach your audience where they are, adapting continuously for optimal results.
              </p>

              <h3 class="text-xl text-accent-500 font-semibold mb-2">Platform-Agnostic, Sustainability-Focused</h3>
              <p class="mb-4">
                We select tools and platforms based on your needs and sustainability goals, ensuring value without pushing a specific technology or service.
              </p>

              <h3 class="text-xl text-accent-500 font-semibold mb-2">Sustainable Growth, No Quick Fixes</h3>
              <p class="mb-4">
                We build long-term strategies that deliver lasting results. All decisions are grounded in sustainable practices to ensure meaningful impact.
              </p>

              <h3 class="text-xl text-accent-500 font-semibold mb-2">Big Insights, Rapid Iteration</h3>
              <p class="mb-4">
                Using agile principles, we test, gather insights, and refine. Our adaptive approach ensures campaigns and strategies evolve alongside your needs.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-xl">
              <img src="/images/esg.png" alt="Digital and sustainable expertise" class="w-full h-auto" />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Call to Action -->
        <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-6">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">Transform Your Space Marketing with Green Orbit Digital</h2>
          <p class="mb-6">
            Our mission is to blend innovative marketing with sustainability. We help space organisations grow responsibly while delivering measurable impact.
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-6">
            <li>Free, no-obligation consultation</li>
            <li>Expert advice on integrating sustainability into your strategy</li>
            <li>Tailored marketing plan aligned with your goals</li>
            <li>A trusted partner delivering measurable results</li>
          </ul>
          <CTA text="Schedule a Call" link="/contact" client:load />
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>